section2.section3:
®PROCESS;
<attribute> <name>the name of the attribute</name> <desc>a natural-language description of the connection method</desc> <value>the syntax or datatype of the attribute value</value> <doc>the document in which the connection method is specified</doc> </attribute>
The registrant may register more than one attribute at a time, each contained in a separate <attribute/> element.
